        public boolean asBoolean(boolean defaultValue)
        Description copied from class: AbstractDynamicValue
        Returns the encapsulated object as a boolean primitive if it is an instance of Boolean, defaultValue otherwise. This method is the equivalent of calling as(Boolean.class, defaultValue).booleanValue().

        This implementation always returns defaultValue; subclasses should override.
